@@ -1,6 +1,14 @@
 # BeforeUnloadJavaScriptDialog Object
 
 * `type` string - Can be `beforeunload`.
+* `frame` [WebFrameMain](../web-frame-main.md) - The frame that requested the
+  JavaScript dialog.
+* `messageText` string - The dialog message text.
+* `url` string - The last committed URL of the frame that requested the dialog.
+* `isMainFrame` boolean - Whether the frame that requested the dialog is the
+  main frame.
+* `isReload` boolean - Whether the `beforeunload` dialog was triggered by a
+  reload.
 * `leave` Function\<boolean\> - Ignores the page's `beforeunload` prevention and
   continues unloading the page. Returns `true` if the dialog was handled by this
   call, otherwise `false`.
