@@ -1,6 +1,13 @@
 # PromptJavaScriptDialog Object
 
 * `type` string - Can be `prompt`.
+* `frame` [WebFrameMain](../web-frame-main.md) - The frame that requested the
+  JavaScript dialog.
+* `messageText` string - The dialog message text.
+* `defaultPromptText` string - The default text for the prompt dialog.
+* `url` string - The last committed URL of the frame that requested the dialog.
+* `isMainFrame` boolean - Whether the frame that requested the dialog is the
+  main frame.
 * `submit` Function\<boolean\> - Closes the prompt dialog and returns `value` to
   the renderer. Returns `true` if the dialog was handled by this call, otherwise
   `false`.
